description:
the date picker displays absolute calendar months.  When you're in say end of January and the default expiry is on 16 February, you'd like to see the January days you can pick as well.  That way you don't need to  go back 1 month to select a date in January.

Requires small modifications to the same files as were needed for ticket #820.

These two options need to be set:

                $("#datepicker" ).datepicker( "option", "showOtherMonths", true );
                $("#datepicker" ).datepicker( "option", "selectOtherMonths", true );

